# Environment Variables Template for Production

## Backend (Render) Environment Variables:
SECRET_KEY=your-new-secret-key-generate-one
DEBUG=False
DATABASE_URL=your-supabase-connection-string
ALLOWED_HOSTS=your-backend-domain.onrender.com
CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=https://your-frontend-domain.vercel.app
PYTHON_VERSION=3.11

## To get your DATABASE_URL from Supabase:
# Format: postgresql://USER:PASSWORD@HOST:PORT/DATABASE
# Example: postgresql://postgres.xxxx:password@aws-0-us-west-1.pooler.supabase.com:6543/postgres

## Frontend (Vercel) Environment Variables:
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://your-backend-domain.onrender.com

## How to generate SECRET_KEY:
# Run in Python: from django.core.management.utils import get_random_secret_key; print(get_random_secret_key())
